content.html: Being non-binary for me is not about moving away from femininity but rather embracing my masculinity & everything in between. Through this I've realised a lot of trans and enby people are better described as "more than" binary (And can bring expansive versions of joy & beauty!)
content.value:
Being non-binary for me is not about moving away from femininity but rather embracing my masculinity & everything in between.

Through this I've realised a lot of trans and enby people are better described as "more than" binary

(And can bring expansive versions of joy & beauty!)
